# Architecture

- Preserve multi-workload federated compute (train, LoRA, jobs) — not “FL library only.”
- Control plane metadata vs data-plane artifacts; do not add new production paths that ship large tensors as nested JSON.
- Default `METADATA_BACKEND=json` for local demo; Postgres behind an explicit flag.
- No authoritative coordination state only in process memory for new features — persist or document as prototype.
- Feature-flag migrations; never silently discard JSON state.
- Public landing may call anonymized `/dashboard/activity` only; ops detail requires operator auth.
